msgid ""
"Names within a node (e.g. topics/services) can be remapped using the "
"syntax ``-r <old name>:=<new name>``. The name/namespace of the node "
"itself can be remapped using ``-r __node:=<new node name>`` and ``-r "
"__ns:=<new node namespace>``."
msgstr ""

